# Poke 芒 Mobile 🛒✨

A React Native mobile app — the natural extension of my Next.js Pokémon e-commerce web project!

Most web features are ported here to take full advantage of mobile conveniences like on-the-go access.

## Why React Native? 📱

Websites rely on HTML/CSS elements, but React Native uses native components that feel truly integrated with iOS and Android.
**Big win**: One codebase runs on both platforms — no separate iOS and Android apps needed!

## Built Almost Entirely with AI 🚀

Most features already existed in the Next.js version, so this was mainly about swapping `<div>` for `<View>`, `<p>` for `<Text>`, etc.
AI sped things up dramatically — from ~10 days of manual work down to just ~2 days.
(The only real learning curve was mastering Expo Router!)

## What Makes Mobile Special

The real magic comes from mobility: use the app anytime, anywhere — no laptop required.
This unlocks powerful features websites struggle with:
- Live GPS (latitude & longitude tracking)
- Camera for instant photo uploads
- Live chat with other users
- Push notifications & more

All of this makes a dedicated mobile app well worth building.

